00:19:16.392 --> 00:19:18.127
What's happening?

00:19:20.729 --> 00:19:23.365
Dear Mom, and Dad, and everybody,

00:19:23.365 --> 00:19:26.168
I'm sorry to leave
without saying goodbye.

00:19:26.168 --> 00:19:27.570
I knew if I said anything,

00:19:27.570 --> 00:19:31.006
you'd try and stop me from trying
to travel to Sonic's world.

00:19:31.006 --> 00:19:33.008
It's very important to me,

00:19:33.008 --> 00:19:34.977
so I hope you'll understand.

00:19:34.977 --> 00:19:36.478
Don't worry.

00:19:36.478 --> 00:19:38.013
I'll be fine.

00:19:38.013 --> 00:19:40.349
And, I'll be back.

00:19:40.349 --> 00:19:41.684
I'll miss you all.

00:19:41.684 --> 00:19:47.122
Mom, and Dad, Grandpa, Danny,
Francis, and Helen...

00:19:47.790 --> 00:19:49.091
I love you.

00:19:49.091 --> 00:19:50.259
Chris

00:19:50.259 --> 00:19:53.562
P.S. I'll tell Sonic and the
others you said "hello."

00:20:26.328 --> 00:20:28.097
[All gasping]

00:20:33.068 --> 00:20:34.837
Hey, that's Chris!

00:20:34.837 --> 00:20:36.105
It worked!

00:20:36.805 --> 00:20:38.774
I did it!

00:20:38.774 --> 00:20:40.643
I actually did it!

00:20:40.643 --> 00:20:42.578
Sonic!

00:20:43.012 --> 00:20:44.380
[Groan]

